high_descs: Walk forward through the door ahead, into the closet, and over to the cardboard box with the spoon inside.
Pick up the spoon from the box and then close the lid of the box.
Walk out of the closet, go through the door that is ahead and slightly to the right into the bathroom, and walk over to the sink.
Place the spoon in the left side of the bathroom sink, run the water, turn off the water, and then pick the spoon back up.
Walk out of the bathroom, make a right in the hallway, then walk into the living room and over to the coffeetable in front of the orange couch.
Place the spoon on the right corner of the coffeetable, while facing the couch, that is on the side not facing the couch.
anns.task_desc: Place the Spoon that was stored in the closet onto the CoffeeTable.

Place the spoon on the coffeetable.
